title: Exclusive: Facebook says Apple rejected its attempt to tell users about App Store fees
text: Facebook Inc on Thursday told Reuters that Apple Inc rejected its attempt to tell users the iPhone maker would take a 30% cut of sales in a new online events feature, forcing Facebook to remove the message to get the tool to users.
